We were super lucky to test out the Twisted Healthy Treats Lick 99%  Sugar Free Sticks Range. 🍦

Naturally, the kids went straight for the Rich Chocolate…
Blinked once and they were gone.

Creamy chocolate ice cream dipped in sugar-free minty choc? 
YES PLEASE 🙌
Not too sweet, super satisfying, 
Creating a delicious blend without being over powering but highlighting both incredible flavours. 

A minty match made in snack heaven with zero regrets!! 

The best part!? 

✅ Zero Added Sugar 
✅ 100% Aussie Dairy & Coconut Cream 🥛 🥥 
✅ Gluten Free 

Perfect for surviving snack time without a sugar rush even in winter in North Queensland :) 

These are a solid win👏 👏🏻
